{"tid":1232044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣前電競選手Dinter對送中條例表態","createTime":"2019-06-16T14:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T06:32:26.000Z","uid":212063,"like":175,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"de6b4c88fe94a0378bf079f48ca80fed2e8b0846","tid":1232044,"uid":212063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:24:57.000Z","msg":"片入邊講<br />\n被Ban台就Ban台<br />\n被解約就解約<br />\n該説的話就要説<br />\n你現在不説以後就沒機會説了<br />\n一個台灣人都可以咁願意去講自己對於呢件事嘅睇法<br />\n淨係呢一點都好值得去Respect<br />\n講得出香港嘅唔同問題<br />\n反觀香港有幾多人跟本連理都唔想理呢件事<br />\n話自己政治冷感就得過且過<br />\n睇到個假香港人toyz就知啦<br />\n連世界各地啲人都聲援我地<br />\n但香港咁多人唔去諗<br />\n繼續去旅行去玩去開心<br />\n對於呢一切嘅一切都無動於衷<br />\n作為一個香港人 我真係好慚愧<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_LXf-F0VHYk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_LXf-F0VHYk&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPgKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=04764367\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_LXf-F0VHYk</a>"},{"pid":"83cab48265bb7d78e14064fb7d5f2a34e245fbce","tid":1232044,"uid":212063,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:25:26.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"f22df3e084fcffecbc1f0487dae2e1650cc1a46f","tid":1232044,"uid":247639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:28:14.000Z","msg":"直輕二推 我推再推"},{"pid":"d364118d799d43744a2d5f47a88a1113d77e8a35","tid":1232044,"uid":136741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:29:24.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇左條片 估唔到佢會講 宜家令更加多人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86873fb9207d06c748e4fc43b9f8ce87b651f54c","tid":1232044,"uid":9394,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:29:35.000Z","msg":"前隊友胎屎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545c4cc127390fc1c9a3a7a9363f92ff8233